OL,3,CNightclub to close its doors for final
OL,4,Ctime after almost 50 years
OL,6,FA much-loved nightclub on the
OL,7,Foutskirts of Bristol has announced its
OL,8,Fclosure after almost 50 years.
OL,10,FChasers, in Kingswood, will close its
OL,11,Fdoors for the final time on Christmas
OL,12,FEve.
OL,14,FIts owners have blamed the closure on
OL,15,Frising costs, a lack of footfall and a
OL,16,Fdecline in club-goers.
