OL,3,CNightclub to close its doors for final
OL,4,Ctime after almost 50 years
OL,6,FThe club has been much-loved by people
OL,7,Fin Kingswood and beyond for years, and
OL,8,Fis even believed to have inspired the
OL,9,Ffictional 'Chasers' in hit sitcom The
OL,10,FOffice.
OL,12,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,13,FKingswood club said: "After close to
OL,14,Ffive decades and four generations of
OL,15,Fthe same family stepping foot inside
OL,16,Fthe building, the decision has been
OL,17,Fmade to end what you all know as
OL,18,FChasers nightclub for good.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
