OL,3,CNightclub to close its doors for final
OL,4,Ctime after almost 50 years
OL,6,F"On a personal level we are saddened
OL,7,Ffor Kingswood, we are saddened for all
OL,8,Fof the staff and we are saddened for
OL,9,Fthe other venues struggling in
OL,10,Fhospitality.
OL,12,FThe closure of Chasers follows similar
OL,13,Fstruggles by other Bristol venues in
OL,14,Fthe past year.
OL,16,FIn May, Gravity nightclub in Clifton
OL,17,Fshut down due to "economic strains"
OL,18,Fand "increasing expenses," according
OL,19,Fto its bosses.
