OL,4,Ctime after almost 50 years
OL,6,FThey also pointed to "regulatory fees
OL,7,Fand the overarching costs inherent to
OL,8,Fthe hospitality world".
OL,10,FIn a survey done in August 2023 by
OL,11,Fnightclub operator Rekom, it was found
OL,12,Fthat younger people are increasingly
OL,13,Fcutting back on nights out due to the
OL,14,Fcost of living crisis.
OL,16,FChasers will close for the majority of
OL,17,FNovember but will be open on every
OL,18,FSaturday of December until its final
OL,19,Fnight on Christmas Eve.
